Topic: Contact Manager

Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviations
Contact Manager          The name of the website

Funtional Requirement
1 Contacts
1.1 The user should be able to add, view, edit, delete contacts.
1.2 This app should support multiple phone numbers
1.3 Support adding a photo label for a contact
1.4 Search contacts by contact name
1.5 Blacklist (block SMS and Phones), add/view/edit/delete
1.6 Directly make phone calls and send SMS from a contact view

2 Contacts Organization
2.1 Manage contact groups
2.2 Sort contacts by name / group name in alphabetical order
2.3 Be able to find specific letter group by tapping the letter on the screen
2.4 Be able to stick your own info to the top
2.5 
